@startuml
[*] --> Registered
Registered --> Validated : validation successful
Validated --> LoggedIn : login

LoggedIn --> Dashboard : open dashboard
Dashboard --> TicketStatus : check ticket status
TicketBooking --> WaitingPayment : book ticket
WaitingPayment --> PaymentConfirmed : payment confirmed
PaymentConfirmed --> OrderComplete : order completed successfully
OrderComplete --> AccountManagement : manage account details
AccountManagement --> Dashboard : back to dashboard
Dashboard --> Logout : logout

Logout --> [*] : end session
@enduml
